<br>
All I can say about last night was that it was a mess.<br>
<br>
Dulcette, you did the best you could with what you had and I for one thought you were very patient to last as long as you did.<br>
<br>
To answer your questions Worst, no Thor never got invited into the chat group although it was requested several times. I was trying to relay what we were doing to him verbaly as best I could.<br>
